SKILLS ACQUIRED:
  Module 1: Network Fundamentals (IP, DNS, connectivity)
  Module 2: Troubleshooting (diagnosis, tcpdump, traceroute)
  Module 3: Docker Networking (bridges, custom networks, multi-network)
  Module 4: Security (isolation, segmentation, monitoring)

NEXT STEPS:
  1. Practice these techniques in your own projects
  2. Explore overlay networks for multi-host setups
  3. Apply segmentation to your Docker Compose files
  4. Set up real monitoring with Prometheus/Grafana

